<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-02-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-02-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="148" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d148">
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Rio de
                                    Janeiro</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-02-19"><hi rend="italic">February 19, 1894</hi></date>.
                            (Received February 19.)</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mr. Thompson announces the arrival on the preceding day of the <hi rend="italic">Nictheroy</hi>, which proceeded in a southerly direction
                        after landing several hundred men at the entrance of the harbor.</p>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>